{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770988379,"nonce":"eShwQoJmIvntYbyFAIT7zV/E10k=","title":"Staff-created borrowers don't receive confirmation email","message":"When staff creates a borrower via the admin form (BorrowersController#create), no confirmation email is sent. The borrower shows as unconfirmed (tos_accepted=false) with no way to verify their email address or accept TOS.\n\nThe self-registration flow (BorrowersController#self_create) correctly calls send_confirmation_pending_email, but the staff flow skips it. Staff-created borrowers should also receive the confirmation email so they can verify their email and accept TOS.","files":null}]}